    University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign

    The University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign is a world leader in research, teaching and public engagement, distinguished by the breadth of its programs, broad academic excellence, and internationally renowned faculty and alumni. Illinois serves the world by creating knowledge, preparing students for lives of impact, and finding solutions to critical societal needs.

    Degrees + Certificates

    Master of Science in Management (iMSM)

    Get an M.S. in Management from the University of Illinois, and learn critical leadership and business skills for the next step in your executive career path.

    Master of Computer Science

    Offered by University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign. Deepen your computer science knowledge and accelerate your career with a top ranked computer science program for computing professionals.

    Master of Science in Accountancy (iMSA)

    Offered by University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign. A cutting-edge degree from an accounting powerhouse, completely online.

    Master of Business Administration (iMBA)

    Offered by University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign. A flexible, affordable, and highly interactive premier online MBA.

    Master of Computer Science in Data Science

    Offered by Universiy of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign. Accelerate your career with a flexible, fully-accredited professional Master of Computer Science in Data Science from one of the worlds top programs.

    Accounting Foundations Graduate Certificate

    Gain in-demand technical knowledge and professional skills to launch a career in accounting or finance.

    CPA Pathways Graduate Certificate

    Prepare for the CPA Exam in a graduate certificate program that builds on your skill set and gets you job ready.

    Graduate Certificate in Accounting Data Analytics

    Learn and practice skills for solving accounting and business challenges, with on-demand content and live classes designed to support career impact and advancement.

    Graduate Certificate in Strategic Leadership & Management

    Develop strong, leading-edge and actionable knowledge and skills for managing people and teams and for developing and implementing organizational strategyall from a top-ranked business school.

    Graduate Certificate in Digital Marketing

    Master strategic marketing concepts that will help you attract more customers and measure impact.

    Instructional Design MasterTrack Certificate

    Become an instructional designer in four months by mastering the art and science of learning.
